org.epics.pvmanager

Interface Collector<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type written in the collector
    O - the type read from the collector
    All Superinterfaces:
    ReadFunction<O>, WriteFunction<I>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheCollector, LatestValueCollector, QueueCollector

    public interface Collector<I,O>
extends WriteFunction<I>, ReadFunction<O>
    A collector can be written from one thread and read from another and provides the point where two subsystems and their rate can be decoupled.
    Author:
    carcassi
